legal.privacySection1Body:
We may collect:

• The email address associated with your account;
• Service usage information (credits consumed, processing history, preferences);
• Images and files uploaded for processing;
• Payment information processed through Stripe.

We do not sell or commercialize your personal data.

legal.privacySection2Body:
Uploaded images and files are used solely to provide the services you request.

• We do not use images to train AI models;
• We do not use images for advertising, marketing, or profiling;
• Files are deleted automatically after 24 hours.

legal.privacySection5Body:
We use the following to deliver the service:

• Supabase (authentication, database, and storage);
• Stripe (payment processing);
• Replicate (AI processing).

These providers process data only to the extent necessary to deliver their services.
